{"tid":1227801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行絕對冇問題","createTime":"2019-06-15T15:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T16:12:33.000Z","uid":247911,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"75073010b3fa12a4116f3f1919aa011a5117ae00","tid":1227801,"uid":247911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"但係你地仲係有人想排斥遊行以外嘅抗爭咁<br />\n仲講咩會俾位人入，成功係因為光環<br />\n<br />\n係咪已經唔記得咗上星期個百萬人遊行得到咩回應？林鄭條柒婆今日講過d咩？<br />\n<br />\n未達到呢三個目標前，我地都唔可以因爲佢所謂暫緩呢d小恩小惠而暫緩所有抗爭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGHGkOr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGHGkOr.png&h=c3ec1eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係淨係講緊衝唔衝嘅問題，係仲有罷工罷課，集會等等<br />\n同埋要畀個限期佢，冇得拖延，否則輸嘅只會係我地"},{"pid":"629262df32929eb93ebe558e70405c86475a3b40","tid":1227801,"uid":247911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:44:42.000Z","msg":"而家出咗人命，我地更加唔可以打消耗戰<br />\n我都唔係主張鳩衝，而係唔可以同所有抗爭割蓆"},{"pid":"5deb1061652f7283c07f2487bdd363c84ae024b6","tid":1227801,"uid":247911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"badf9026554a216ebecc1ea03bf93680cea94105","tid":1227801,"uid":221919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:59:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cadc6ca8d33a08b3d32d9fca920f724940b466c","tid":1227801,"uid":247911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301f0e351232861bea41b0356c0d5fdd74756426","tid":1227801,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:04:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e8db41a547d000ed1d91e48d1a9190caa627d7b","tid":1227801,"uid":247911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets